Description:
Garfield Kart - Play as Garfield and his friends in a funny and fast racing! For whom you want to play? Garfield, Odie, Jon, Nerman ... you choose. Take part in a crazy race in multiplayer mode or against the computer. Challenge your friends, thanks to the platform-independant multiplayer mode. Use your best driving skills and power-ups to be number one at the finish line!
